{"tid":1931980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"瓏瓏貨van  大把時間傾果位會員請進","createTime":"2020-03-18T12:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T14:05:42.000Z","uid":20809,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"99d6723dcb2a0e5daa54d1308483a92d9631ca2e","tid":1931980,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:30:08.000Z","msg":"咁岩1001開返個post承上，唔覆你怕你自以為辯論了得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0576057abee207c47f1610f50afaa2d506a5c4fb","tid":1931980,"uid":20809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:33:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">1.樓主有講，最貴都係月費300蚊，做到幾多都司機自己袋<br />\n<br />\n2&amp;3.popo有大水喉照住，一開始畀低價同優惠吸大客，頂死哂其他台，成功壟斷市場之後就抽司機勁多佣，啲單又喺哂popo度，點走？<br />\n所以popovan啲司機質素咪差囉<br />\n不過你未call過唔會知分别<br />\n<br />\n大把時間同你傾</span><br />\n<br />\n咩叫點走？簽撚左約一定要用popo van?<br />\n市場講供求，popo van養唔掂d司機，d司機要蝕本都唔會有人做，冇人做司機，顧客就難call車，自然會慢慢淘汰，事實依家冇wo,尋日先call完，倒數唔洗十秒已經俾人接左，咁反映左d咩？你大把時間可以諗諗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次你講質素，喂依家我想要由a點車架餐去b點咋，要咩質素呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又或者可以想要求咩質素呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通c4v司機靚仔d大隻d,定係渣車快d穩d呀，講到冇野講講質素，要質素我call乜鳩貨van呀，叫順豐上門收啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇興趣知你有幾多時間同我傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff2caa2c58f0628bea40e3ce1ef370931c6aeae","tid":1931980,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:33:42.000Z","msg":"幫你貼埋過黎，廢事你唔記得自己講過乜"},{"pid":"db268cf88cbf0a5c064cfb0c3c3d570a673fdd6f","tid":1931980,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:49:22.000Z","msg":"黎啦，唔好係果個post尾聲就串柒柒，新post就笠晒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85806f8db0f6d8f5f74b92f2fff352f979bbd6e1","tid":1931980,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b14869a0c52a877f602c39b7433b63fdba574f","tid":1931980,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7a5cec2eaba4b310f11180f80f6e54aa194dc6","tid":1931980,"uid":233835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:31:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>hktvmall 本身有車隊佢地有搵 C4V 傾合作<br />\n只係個價錢太低 ( 仲衰過 SF )<br />\nC4V 老闆要保障手足而推左<br />\n<br />\nhktvmall 同 龍門老闆一樣 <br />\n計數計到好足，商人一個<br />\n當你知道唔係咩都講道義果陣，咁你就有機會出黎做生意</blockquote>不意外，做生意係咁㗎啦<br />\n成班小學雞一定要人哋做慈善<br />\n點維持到落去啊</blockquote>做生意錢一定要賺<br />\n小弟都係做生意<br />\n但係佢講自己咁偉大呢下頂唔順<br />\n<br />\n又話做左幾多野蝕幾多十萬百萬<br />\n但係一連開兩間分店？<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢呢個business model 唔理想<br />\n<br />\nbtw 龍門老闆係有問過C4V老闆貨van呢行係點樣做<br />\n如果淨係做自己外賣，需要嗎？</blockquote>淨係自己公司嗰幾間鋪嘅外賣車，仲要內部用，有需要特登寫個app咩？</blockquote>你最心水清"},{"pid":"b0aed1a436400afd70562627afc736a35fd274ce","tid":1931980,"uid":233835,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為有員工唔小心call左popovan <br />\n令到有客人食唔到盤菜就要開條車隊出黎<br />\n<br />\n咁廚房買唔到食油就一定要去中東買個油田<br />\n起提煉工廠<br />\n直送龍門<br />\n<br />\n一定係</blockquote>駁唔到</blockquote><br />\n搵d盲粉黎駁我啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" clas